OL,3,CSNP whip removed from MSP following
OL,4,C'utterly abhorrent' Gaza comments
OL,6,FAn SNP MSP has had the whip removed
OL,7,Ffollowing "utterly abhorrent" comments
OL,8,Fabout the Israel-Hamas conflict.
OL,10,FThe party confirmed it has taken
OL,11,Faction following social media comments
OL,12,Ffrom Glasgow Shettleston MSP John
OL,13,FMason.
OL,15,FThe whip has been removed with
OL,16,F"immediate effect", officials said.
