OL,3,CSNP whip removed from MSP following
OL,4,C'utterly abhorrent' Gaza comments
OL,6,FIt comes after Mr Mason reacted to
OL,7,Fcriticism over Scottish External
OL,8,FAffairs Secretary Angus Robertson's
OL,9,Fmeeting with Israel's deputy
OL,10,Fambassador Daniela Grudsky.
OL,12,FMr Mason had also met with the Israeli
OL,13,Fambassador and attracted fury from
OL,14,Fmembers of his own party after he
OL,15,Fposted on social media: "If Israel
OL,16,Fwanted to commit genocide, they would
OL,17,Fhave killed ten times as many."
