OL,3,CSNP whip removed from MSP following
OL,4,C'utterly abhorrent' Gaza comments
OL,6,FIt was in response to former SNP MSP
OL,7,FSandra White, who said: "We know what
OL,8,FIsraelis hope to achieve they are
OL,9,Falready committing genocide in Gaza",
OL,10,Fadding that "innocent children are
OL,11,Fbeing massacred".
OL,13,FRemoving the whip from Mr Mason, a
OL,14,Fparty spokesperson said: "To
OL,15,Fflippantly dismiss the death of more
OL,16,Fthan 40,000 Palestinians is completely
OL,17,Funacceptable. There can be no room in
OL,18,Fthe SNP for this kind of intolerance.
