OL,3,CSNP whip removed from MSP following
OL,4,C'utterly abhorrent' Gaza comments
OL,6,F"The chief whip has today withdrawn
OL,7,Fthe whip from John Mason MSP with
OL,8,Fimmediate effect, pending internal
OL,9,FParliamentary group due process.
OL,11,F"The SNP group will now meet to
OL,12,Fdiscuss the matter, with a
OL,13,Frecommendation that the whip be
OL,14,Fsuspended from John Mason for a fixed
OL,15,Fperiod of time because of this utterly
OL,16,Fabhorrent comment."
