OL,3,CSNP whip removed from MSP following
OL,4,C'utterly abhorrent' Gaza comments
OL,6,FFormer SNP Westminster leader Ian
OL,7,FBlackford criticised Mr Mason, saying
OL,8,Fon X: "Forty thousand plus dead in
OL,9,FGaza and you tweet this. You are not
OL,10,Ffit for public office. You are an
OL,11,Fembarrassment and not fit to represent
OL,12,Fanyone. You glorify killing and murder
OL,13,Fwith your obtuse comment. Just go and
OL,14,Fdo it now."
OL,16,FScottish First Minister John Swinney
OL,17,Fsaid Mr Robertson's meeting with Ms
OL,18,FGrudsky was "necessary" and allowed
OL,19,Fthe Scottish government to put across
OL,20,Fthe need for an "immediate ceasefire"
OL,21,Fin Gaza.
